**Target Aspect Ratio:** --ar 16:9
**Style:** Editorial / Lifestyle Photography.
**Structure:**
"Keep the product in the image unchanged. **Format: Wide Landscape Banner.** Composition: [CINEMATIC_WIDE_SHOT] with negative space on [LEFT/RIGHT]. Context: [REAL_WORLD_RUSSIAN_SCENARIO] showing the product IN USE. Action: [HUMAN_INTERACTION_OR_PROCESS]. Lighting: [NATURAL_OR_CINEMATIC]. Focus: Authentic storytelling, trust, and lifestyle integration."
